Classification: Documentary
Genre: Drama | Family | Mystery | Thriller
Status: New Series
Network: Biography Channel ( USA)
Airs: Saturdays at 10:00 pm
Runtime: 30 Minutes
Premiere: August 04, 2012

BIO Channel presents “The uneXplained”, a new original series from Executive Producer Doug Liman (“The Bourne Trilogy,” “Mr. and Mrs. Smith”) that explores strange real life cases and individuals who turn to the supernatural world for help when all traditional methods have failed to provide a resolution.
